{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>LiveWar</strong> is an easy-to-pick and hard-to-master strategy game, it's like a simplified version of a Company of Heroes, Men Of War, Wargame, or some other RTS-like game where you play as a senior commander who deploys the most reasonable units and skills at the right time for the situation on the battlefield, and then watches your army destroy the enemy. Of course, if necessary, you can also summon air strikes, missiles, or directly command officers to turn the tide.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Operation Friendly</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Focus on strategy</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">What you see is what you get\u00a0battlefield information</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Real-time and vivid policy feedback</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3519630/extras/Desc_1.gif?t=1740065940\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Diverse Units &amp; Deep Strategies</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Up to dozens of units</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Various unique skills, such as summoning air strikes, setting up cover, resource buildings, etc</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The various types of units mutually counter each other.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3519630/extras/Desc_2_2.gif?t=1740065940\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Additional options--Commanders</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Commanders with distinct personalities</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Commanders have their own unique attributes and skills, and they are good at specific aspects such as offense, defense, air defense, anti-armor, etc</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Commanders are almost the only unit type that can be directly controlled by the player</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Commanders can give bonuses to nearby units, so the combination of commander and unit is crucial</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3519630/extras/Desc_3.gif?t=1740065940\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Rich contents</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Maps of different styles</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Management outside of combat</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Research and development or purchase of technology bonuses</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3519630/extras/Desc_4.gif?t=1740065940\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p>","background":"https://store.akamai.steamstatic.com/images/storepagebackground/app/3519630?t=1740065940","background_raw":"https://store.akamai.steamstatic.com/images/storepagebackground/app/3519630?t=1740065940","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3519630/b68381cc7213420fed8bed1840793e96777f02bb/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1740065940","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3519630/b68381cc7213420fed8bed1840793e96777f02bb/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1740065940","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Steam Achievements","id":22},{"description":"Full controller support","id":28},{"description":"Family Sharing","id":62}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[],"notes":null},"controller_support":"full","detailed_description":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>LiveWar</strong> is an easy-to-pick and hard-to-master strategy game, it's like a simplified version of a Company of Heroes, Men